	<!-- Introduction -->
	<!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
	<purpose>
		<p>
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
representation of conditions established during design phase on the use of occurrences of components in products offered to market.
These conditions relate to the serial number, the production lot number or the production date of the proposed products.
   </p>
	</purpose>
	<!-- Items in scope -->
	<inscope>
		<li>serial number-based condition for the use of a component in a product proposed to market;</li>
		<li>production lot number-based condition for the use of a component in a product proposed to market;</li>
		<li>production date-based condition for the use of a component in a product proposed to market.</li>
	</inscope>
